# First Time Setup of a new AAD(Azure Active Directory)
* You need to setup a Subscription applied to an Azure Active Directory Resource

**Creating A new Azure AD Resource**
Sign in > "Create a resource" > "Identity" > "Azure Active Directory"

**Apply a Subscription**
* If you have already have a subscription and it is applied to a different resource you can't fully manage you can re-apply it
Cost Management > Billing > Subscriptions > 
